OL,3,CTrain station advertising board turned
OL,4,Coff following criticism and
OL,5,Covercrowding
OL,7,FNetwork Rail has turned off a large
OL,8,Fadvertising board at London's Euston
OL,9,Fstation following criticism it made
OL,10,Fthe passenger experience worse.
OL,12,FThe Government-owned company said
OL,13,Freviewing how the screen is used is
OL,14,Fpart of a five-point plan aimed at
OL,15,Fimproving the station.
OL,17,FOther measures include creating more
OL,18,Fconcourse space and enhancing how the
OL,19,Fstation operates during disruption.
