OL,3,CTrain station advertising board turned
OL,4,Coff following criticism and
OL,5,Covercrowding
OL,7,FNetwork Rail, which owns the station,
OL,8,Fhas been criticised for converting the
OL,9,Fmain concourse departure board into a
OL,10,Flarge advertising screen, with smaller
OL,11,Ftrain information boards installed.
OL,13,FEarlier this week watchdog London
OL,14,FTravelWatch warned that passengers at
OL,15,FEuston are being put "in danger" by
OL,16,F"high levels of overcrowding".
OL,18,FIt said "last-minute announcements"
OL,19,Fmean passengers "rush to platforms",
OL,20,Fand staff "appear overwhelmed by the
OL,21,Fsheer numbers of people".
