OL,7,FNetwork Rail said its "senior
OL,8,Fmanagement" have been asked to meet
OL,9,FTransport Secretary Louise Haigh next
OL,10,Fweek to "answer questions on plans for
OL,11,Fthe station and set out a route
OL,12,Ftowards longer-term improvements".
OL,14,FMs Haigh said: "For too long, Euston
OL,15,Fstation simply hasn't been good enough
OL,16,Ffor passengers.
OL,18,F"That's why I've tasked Network Rail
OL,19,Fwith coming up with a clear plan to
OL,20,Fimmediately improve conditions for
OL,21,Fpassengers.
