OL,7,F"This includes a shutdown of the
OL,8,Fadvertising boards from today to
OL,9,Freview their use.
OL,11,F"We know Euston needs a permanent
OL,12,Fsolution and are working hard to agree
OL,13,Fthis ` but these immediate steps will
OL,14,Fhelp to alleviate some of the issues
OL,15,Fthe station has been facing."
OL,17,FNetwork Rail route director Gary Walsh
OL,18,Fsaid: "Passengers haven't received the
OL,19,Fexperience they deserve at Euston
OL,20,Frecently and we need to do better.
